545
00:44:49,840 --> 00:44:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] Znači to je bila novogodišnja odluka.

546
00:44:52,639 --> 00:44:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ja kad pogledam, tamo piše 2021.

547
00:44:58,000 --> 00:45:00,320
