561
00:45:40,880 --> 00:45:41,679
[SPEAKER_00] Kaos je bio napravljen.

562
00:45:41,840 --> 00:45:43,199
[SPEAKER_01] Iz garaže i iz garzanjeri.

563
00:45:43,599 --> 00:45:43,840
